data.description: Welcome to the sought-after PNG ISD. Don't miss out on this remarkable opportunity to add this gem to your portfolio. With its modern improvements, sought-after location, and undeniable potential, this property is poised to deliver both short-term or long-term returns on your investment. Location is key, and this home has it all. Nestled within a highly popular subdivision, it offers a sense of community and a desirable neighborhood atmosphere. Convenience is at your fingertips with a location that provides easy access to local amenities, schools, shopping centers, and more. With a host of other desirable features, this home checks allthe boxes for those seeking a perfect blend of style, functionality, and investment potential. Sale is being professionally processed by a third party. Buyer Responsible for Processing Fee of $6,500. Please review “Presentation of Offers” document before submitting offer. Property sold as-is. Calling all investors!
